{"tid":2429753,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民：熱狗仲衰過陶君行","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T14:10:39.000Z","uid":201464,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"53f389856593a724601a2dea6a0f47694443e601","tid":2429753,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"黃毓民：<br />\n<br />\n我曾經批評35+，但我好反對泛民因為35+被控國安法，佢哋完全唔應該受如此迫害。<br />\n但鄭松泰曾詳細解釋點解35+犯國安法，跟本係間接地將國安法合理化。<br />\n<br />\n我而家明確咁講，黃洋達班人（熱狗）仲衰過陶君行，仲衰過以前其他跟過我既人。<br />\n<br />\n表面上，泛民班人明明溫和過鄭松泰同黃洋達。點解而家泛民比人拉哂，鄭松泰同黃洋達會無事？<br />\n<br />\n希望香港朋友得閒可以問候下熱狗佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民 毓民踩場 210301 <br />\n<a href=\"https://myradio.hk/?cat=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyradio.hk%2F%3Fcat%3D2&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=42b63ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myradio.hk/?cat=2</a>"},{"pid":"4864df442ede1f0d9bad98620941026dff3381d7","tid":2429753,"uid":201464,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我而家明確咁講，黃洋達班人（熱狗）仲衰過陶君行，仲衰過以前其他跟過我既人。</span></span>"},{"pid":"86dbfa0726e99954f27d719c8621387e97ef2f52","tid":2429753,"uid":29423,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"今次我就撐碌撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b7fd0e09e6311fb8c71c744e3785d3fc880d34","tid":2429753,"uid":42734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"國共內戰"},{"pid":"ecf923b6d6a3480fec1317aeda3dd9212f76ba05","tid":2429753,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"熱狗：黃毓民黃屍精神病，死泛粉港豬"},{"pid":"274a6db6ac38ea61b93843e1b2b6395fb2bfd250","tid":2429753,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf923b6d6a3480fec1317aeda3dd9212f76ba05","tid":2429753,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"